1
00:00:00,280 --> 00:00:03,600
Mobile devices tend to
use specialized hardware.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,390
Whereas stationary computers tend
to use standardized hardware.

3
00:00:07,390 --> 00:00:11,220
Mobile devices tend to use many
different versions of operating systems.

4
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:14,260
For example, there are many
different versions of Android.

5
00:00:14,260 --> 00:00:18,300
Whereas stationary computers tend
to run Windows, MAC OS or Linux.

6
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:21,260
They also have large storage capacity.

7
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:25,300
On the other hand, mobile devices tend
to have a large number of accessories

8
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:26,940
such as cameras and GPS.
